{"tid":1565194,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本自駕問題","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:01:28.000Z","uid":184995,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5a3dcfdb8602237dd543b566f9f66f5c9176af","tid":1565194,"uid":184995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"十月會同屋企人去旅行<br />\n<br />\n想問下租車問題，因為第一次自駕.<br />\n五位五件行李 - 租Alphard/Serena 呢兩架OK嗎？<br />\n同埋洗唔洗用到TEP? 見Tocoo有TEP plan...係咪toyota直接訂既話無TEP plan?<br />\n<br />\n下行程如下的話 有無咩意見及修改.<br />\n<br />\n11Oct: 名古屋<br />\n12Oct: 高山<br />\n13Oct: 金澤<br />\n14Oct: 富山 (15號早上由立山往黑部。。。應該要用到立山代駕服務)<br />\n15Oct: 大町 (回名古屋前可否走一轉上高地先返落去NGO呢?)<br />\n16Oct: 名古屋<br />\n17Oct: 名古屋<br />\n18Oct: 回港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef4a0be950ed30f3a82c33a3c2307f889aa34bd","tid":1565194,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"中秋自選活動 祝大家平平安安 團團圓圓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n►人鏈活動◄<br />\n1630 石硤尾聯校人鏈&gt;集合點: 黃棣珊中學正門<br />\n1930 屯門牛牛人鏈&gt;集合點: 顯發里對出空地<br />\n2100 將軍澳人鏈&gt;調景嶺站&rarr;單車公園&larr;寶康公園<br />\n2130 沙田城門河人鏈 (直接去最接近你既河邊集合)<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►快閃大合唱◄<br />\n1300 中環&gt;遮打花園<br />\n1300 太古&gt;OIE樓下水池<br />\n1930 屯門&gt;顯發里對出空地<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►獅子山之路，齊慶中秋夜◄<br />\n1900 大圍、樂富、黃大仙等入口集合<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►18區賞燈晚會 ◄ (如無注明則2030開始)<br />\n【新界西】<br />\n屯門顯發里對出空地 (承接大合唱)<br />\n屯門公園<br />\n天水圍公園<br />\n元朗公園<br />\n荃灣公園海濱長廊<br />\n葵涌運動場籃球場，林士德遊樂場<br />\n青衣海濱長廊<br />\n【新界東】<br />\n1900 上水陳融中學旁紅場<br />\n沙田中央公園<br />\n大埔海濱公園 ，大埔中央公園<br />\n馬鞍山公園<br />\n將軍澳海濱公園，寶康公園<br />\n【九龍】<br />\n美孚嶺南之風<br />\n長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗通州街遊樂場<br />\n尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n黃大仙廣場 ，摩士公園<br />\n觀塘海濱公園<br />\n油塘道遊樂場<br />\n2100 紅磡碼頭<br />\n2150 慈雲山中央球場大合唱<br />\n【港島】<br />\n維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌至西灣河海濱長廊<br />\n柴灣公園<br />\n【東涌】<br />\n東涌海濱長廊，百慕達公園<br />\n【離島】<br />\n2115 長洲東灣"},{"pid":"f6b5715d038b895e5e1b90f05d382470857922c1","tid":1565194,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1aaf942a742d8e3139d916d2f7868ad6e5575151","tid":1565194,"uid":150294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"唔建議Alphard, 太大架，日本市區 d 泊車位同香港差唔多窄。我兩次 6 大 1 細自駕遊都係 Noah 搞掂！"},{"pid":"4409e9ccb67a4fce12b01abc9707c57a98902437","tid":1565194,"uid":235074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"高山內街d路有點窄，視乎你的駕車技術決定租大細車<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db85c8a7c4aac0713120d8effe39efb7c3067d2","tid":1565194,"uid":184995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa